nodes.text: Vulture Squad was an armored unit of the Sith Empire Military present during the battle for Corellia in 3627 BBY. Amongst its ranks were heavy battle droids and walkers. Such walkers included Armor Unit 02 and Armor Unit 14, which were destroyed by the Eternal Alliance's Commander during the battle.
